description:
Enpass is a cross-platform password management app to securely store passwords and other credentials in a virtual vault locked with a master password. Unlike most other popular password managers, Enpass is an offline password manager.


What's new
- Family account admins can initiate managing family members access from the accounts page.
- Small bug fixes and performance enhancements.
For Enpass Business Users
- Fixed an issue where vault sharing was not working for some users.
Questions? Visit discussion.enpass.io for help, email support@enpass.io, or tweet @EnpassApp.
